{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Keyword 2: Nightfall, you can put your detective skills to the test in a heart-gripping cyberpunk mystery adventure where every dark corner of an intricate complex vertical city is yours to explore. Scale luxury mansions, scout dangerous slums, interrogate witnesses, collect key evidence, solve murders, and enjoy hotpots. Inspired by the labyrinthine Kowloon Walled City and Chongqing, Keyword 2: Nightfall features stunning urban verticality, offering unique traversal opportunities and hidden discoveries at every turn. Every choice shapes the outcome, leading you closer to the truth, or deeper into the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are Kurt, a skilled detective summoned to a luxurious penthouse in the dead of night, only to be confronted with the shocking murder of the daughter of the city's most influential figure, Jim King.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/title-exploration.png?t=1731696836\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/exploration.gif?t=1731696836\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture into the vertical city and uncover hidden mysteries!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Skyscrapers or slums? As a free-willed detective, the choice is yours.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the shocking truth lurking under the neon glow of this deceptive world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/title-investigation.png?t=1731696836\" />  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/invetsigation.gif?t=1731696836\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Kurt, a detective investigating the shocking murder of the daughter of the city\u2019s most influential figure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Revisit your memories to discover clues hidden in plain sight!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Receive hints at your own pace by engaging with your colleagues and the city's residents.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/title-interview___interrogation.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/interview.gif?t=1731696836\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with characters connected to the murder case, uncovering their lies and piecing together the truth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friend or enemy? Watch their compelling stories unveil as the plot unfolds\u2014numerous side quests await your exploration.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/title-deduction.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deduction.gif?t=1731696836\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use our in-game dashboard to analyze clues and draw logical conclusions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your knowledge and choices will guide you to your own beliefs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/title-chill.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/chill.gif?t=1731696836\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feeling overwhelmed? Take a break and devour some delicious hotpot or wander through the vibrant night market for an unforgettable experience!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a variety of lighthearted mini-games where you can collect medallions to exchange for items!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015470/extras/deviderpng.png?t=1731696836\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will your actions lead you to redemption \u2014 or into deeper darkness?\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you play hardball with evil?\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Does turning a blind eye make you complicit?\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join us on this thrilling journey, and the decision is yours.\u00a0</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite